Where would I go to change the icon of the collapsible?

In your code, you would change the icon by modifying the `ChevronIcon` function in the same file. The `ChevronIcon` function is defined at the bottom of your code snippet and is used inside the `Collapsible.Trigger` component.

Here's exactly where and how you would change it:

```tsx
// Replace this function with your new icon
export function ChevronIcon(props: React.ComponentProps<"svg">) {
    return (
        <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none" {...props}>
            <path d="M3.5 9L7.5 5L3.5 1" stroke="currentcolor" />
        </svg>
    );
